		<title>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.1 Released</title>
		<link>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-1-released/</link>
		<comments>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-1-released/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 18 Jul 2018 18:35:42 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Darryl Hnatiuk]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Andromo App Maker]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Press Release]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[changelog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4381</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.1.1 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Fixed a bug in Audio, Radio and Podcast activities where currently playing audio would fail to automatically resume after an interstitial ad was shown. Fixed incorrect Play/Pause button state after navigating to another activity with the [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-1-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.1 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.1.1 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed a bug in Audio, Radio and Podcast activities where currently playing audio would fail to automatically resume after an interstitial ad was shown.</li>
<li>Fixed incorrect Play/Pause button state after navigating to another activity with the navigation drawer, playing a track, and navigating back.</li>
<li>Made it so media controls are reset to their default states to indicate when audio is loaded/playing in another activity.</li>
<li>Fixed incorrect state of some other media controls after navigating using the navigation drawer (e.g. current time blinking while another activity&#8217;s audio was paused).</li>
<li>Fixed an issue with sms: and smsto: link handling in the Website, Custom Page, and HTML Archive activities causing them to fail with a &#8216;no application found&#8217; error in some cases.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.1 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-4385" src="https://i1.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/becca-tapert-357523-unsplash.jpg?resize=1000%2C667&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/becca-tapert-357523-unsplash.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i1.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/becca-tapert-357523-unsplash.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i1.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/becca-tapert-357523-unsplash.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
