		<title>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.0 Released</title>
		<link>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-0-released/</link>
		<comments>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-0-released/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 05 Jul 2018 14:14:25 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Darryl Hnatiuk]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Andromo App Maker]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Press Release]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Android 8.1]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[api 26]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[api 27]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[api26]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[changelog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4354</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.1.0 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Apps now target Android 8.1 (API level 27) &#8211; one better than Google&#8217;s mandated API 26 target requirement effective August 2018! Changed minimum version requirement to Android 4.1 &#8220;Jelly Bean&#8221; (API level 16). Many (!) changes [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-0-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.0 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.1.0 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Apps now target Android 8.1 (API level 27) &#8211; one better than Google&#8217;s mandated API 26 target requirement effective August 2018!</li>
<li>Changed minimum version requirement to Android 4.1 &#8220;Jelly Bean&#8221; (API level 16).</li>
<li>Many (!) changes to fix and update things that would not work due to changes introduced in Android API 26 and API 27. Many months of work&#8230;</li>
<li>Extensive internal changes to work around new restrictions on background services.</li>
<li>Changes to how audio cache data is accessed to eliminate the risk of TransactionTooLargeException for very large playlists.</li>
<li>Improved audio cache management when switching between activities.</li>
<li>Improved audio cache data storage.</li>
<li>Changes to how &#8220;Download and play&#8221; actions are implemented.</li>
<li>A progress notification is shown while podcast files are downloaded.</li>
<li>Made it so &#8220;Show track info&#8221; works with SHOUTcast stream URLs that end in &#8220;;&#8221; or &#8220;;stream/1&#8221;</li>
<li>Fixed navigating &#8220;back&#8221; to the parent activity after clicking on an audio notification.</li>
<li>Added some missing French language translations.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.0 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-4375" src="https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/kim-s-ly-187663-unsplash.jpg?resize=1000%2C667&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/kim-s-ly-187663-unsplash.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/kim-s-ly-187663-unsplash.jpg?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/kim-s-ly-187663-unsplash.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-1-0-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.1.0 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
