		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4347</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.16 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Fixed a bug where the EU launch notice could fail to be shown on the first launch of the app on some devices. Updated the Google Mobile Ads SDK (AdMob) version to 15.0.1. Updated the YouTube [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-16-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.16 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.16 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed a bug where the EU launch notice could fail to be shown on the first launch of the app on some devices.</li>
<li>Updated the Google Mobile Ads SDK (AdMob) version to 15.0.1.</li>
<li>Updated the YouTube Data API to version v3-rev198-1.23.0.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.16 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
