				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.14 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed missing auto-color background when using &#8220;Grid: square image + title: 3 columns auto-color.&#8221;</li>
<li>Tweaked auto-color grid styles to prevent a thin gap from appearing between the image and the text area on some devices.</li>
<li>Improved the look of auto-color grid styles when a background image is used.</li>
<li>Fixed the Twitter activity&#8217;s &#8216;Tweets from a Twitter List&#8217; mode which wasn&#8217;t working.</li>
<li>Fixed the Podcast Episode activity so the music controls are always visible without needing to be scrolled into view.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.14 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
