		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lorne Laliberte]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Andromo App Maker]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Press Release]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[changelog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4255</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.13 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Added some item styles with a new layout behaviour similar to the &#8220;button grid&#8221; dashboard style from Andromo v4 (&#8220;Grid: square image + side title&#8221;, &#8220;Grid: square image + side title auto-color&#8221;, &#8220;Grid: square image + [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-13-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.13 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.13 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Added some item styles with a new layout behaviour similar to the &#8220;button grid&#8221; dashboard style from Andromo v4 (&#8220;Grid: square image + side title&#8221;, &#8220;Grid: square image + side title auto-color&#8221;, &#8220;Grid: square image + side title subtitle&#8221; and &#8220;Grid: square image + side title subtitle auto-color&#8221;). Note: these styles are automatically adjusted when used with a background image. If a background image exists, the items will be slightly translucent and use a different divider type so the background image remains subtly visible behind the item.</li>
<li>Improved the look of some grid styles when a background image is used.</li>
<li>Improved the quality of images in the Photo Gallery activity when one dimension of the source image is slightly larger than 1024 pixels.</li>
<li>Changed how the audio controls are displayed on right-to-left language devices so they&#8217;re consistent with other audio apps.</li>
<li>Added support for sms: and smsto: in Website, Custom Page, and HTML Archive activities.</li>
<li>Made it so tel: URIs are automatically escaped to preserve special characters such as # for links in Website, Custom Page, and HTML Archive activities.</li>
<li>Added a new &#8220;Add Activity&#8221; dropup button below the Project &gt; Activities list. Reduces the need to scroll up to the top of the page for those people with lots of activities in their projects.</li>
<li>Changed the minimum time between builds of the same project to 15 minutes.</li>
<li>Fixed the account username signup message to read &#8220;Minimum 4 characters&#8221;.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Examples of New Grid Styles</h3>

