		<title>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.12 Released</title>
		<link>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-12-released/</link>
		<comments>https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-12-released/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 13 Mar 2018 19:31:08 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Darryl Hnatiuk]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Andromo App Maker]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Press Release]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[changelog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4237</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.12 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Fixed an issue in the Podcast activity where the audio notification would fail to open the activity if the podcast&#8217;s playlist was large. Fixed an issue with the Set as Wallpaper feature where it would fail [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-12-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.12 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.12 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed an issue in the Podcast activity where the audio notification would fail to open the activity if the podcast&#8217;s playlist was large.</li>
<li>Fixed an issue with the Set as Wallpaper feature where it would fail on some device configurations when the chosen app didn&#8217;t have the appropriate permissions configured.</li>
<li>Implemented several platform security upgrades:
<ul>
<li>Enabled Google Safe Browsing for WebViews (available on Android 5.0 and above).</li>
<li>Made some changes to WebView error handling.</li>
<li>Made it so links are sanitized before being passed on to external apps.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.12 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4166" src="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-5.jpg?resize=600%2C337&#038;ssl=1" alt="Andromo App Maker for Android" width="600" height="337" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-5.jpg?resize=600%2C337&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-5.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-5.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2018/andromo-app-maker-for-android-v5-0-12-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.12 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
