		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4224</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.11 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Updated the Facebook Audience Network SDK to version 4.27.0. Added a time limit for the caching of Facebook Audience Network interstitials. Fixed a bug in the Podcast activity where the download option would fail with an [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2017/andromo-app-maker-android-v5-0-11-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.11 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.11 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Updated the Facebook Audience Network SDK to version 4.27.0.</li>
<li>Added a time limit for the caching of Facebook Audience Network interstitials.</li>
<li>Fixed a bug in the Podcast activity where the download option would fail with an error in certain situations.</li>
<li>Prevented a crash on the About dialog on some Samsung devices when <em>Settings &gt; Target Market</em> was set to <em>Samsung Apps</em>.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.11 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4167" src="https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-6.jpg?resize=600%2C375&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="600" height="375" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-6.jpg?resize=600%2C375&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-6.jpg?resize=768%2C480&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
