		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4212</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.10 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version: Made it so the toolbar is no longer always pinned in landscape orientation; now it is only pinned in landscape if it was pinned in portrait orientation. Fixed an issue in the Twitter activity where text [&#8230;]</p>
