]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.10 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version:</p>
<ul>
<li>Made it so the toolbar is no longer always pinned in landscape orientation; now it is only pinned in landscape if it was pinned in portrait orientation.</li>
<li>Fixed an issue in the Twitter activity where text was being cut off on some Android versions.</li>
<li>Fixed the &#8216;List: wide image (4:3 aspect) + title&#8217; and &#8216;List: wide image (4:3 aspect) + title description&#8217; dashboard item styles where the square image was being referenced instead of the wide image.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.10 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4165" src="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-4.jpg?resize=600%2C450&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="600" height="450" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-4.jpg?resize=600%2C450&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-4.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/andromo-coffee2-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
