				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.8 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version release:</p>
<ul>
<li>Added 6 new background image effect filters: Darken, Lighten, Midnight, Twilight, Greyscale, Tint</li>
<li>Migrated projects created with Andromo v4 that used the old &#8220;Frosting&#8221; and &#8220;Midnight&#8221; image effects (that have not updated their background images since July 27, 2017) to take advantage of the new background image effect filters.</li>
</ul>

<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.8 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
