		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.7 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version release: Added support for Channel IDs to the YouTube activity. Added an option to disable the share item in the Audio Player, Podcast, and Radio activities. Updated the AppBrain SDK to version 13.22. Updated the StartApp [&#8230;]</p>
