				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.7 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version release:</p>
<ul>
<li>Added support for Channel IDs to the YouTube activity.</li>
<li>Added an option to disable the share item in the Audio Player, Podcast, and Radio activities.</li>
<li>Updated the AppBrain SDK to version 13.22.</li>
<li>Updated the StartApp SDK to version 3.6.3.</li>
<li>Added a language translation file for Finnish.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.7 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
