		<category><![CDATA[Press Release]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[changelog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.andromo.com/?p=4147</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Andromo App Maker for Android version 5.0.6 has been released. Here is a list of changes in this version release: Fixed a bug that would occur in large projects (more than 99 activities) where some dashboard and navigation icons would be missing as well as some activities. Fixed a bug in the Radio and Music [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com/2017/andromo-app-maker-android-v5-0-6-released/">Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.6 Released</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://blog.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker Blog</a>.</p>
