				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.andromo.com">Andromo App Maker for Android</a> version 5.0.6 has been released.</p>
<p>Here is a list of changes in this version release:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed a bug that would occur in large projects (more than 99 activities) where some dashboard and navigation icons would be missing as well as some activities.</li>
<li>Fixed a bug in the Radio and Music Player activity where long status text wasn&#8217;t scrolling properly.</li>
<li>Fixed an issue in dashboard grid item styles where the column count was not adjusting properly in landscape orientation.</li>
</ul>
<p>Andromo App Maker for Android v5.0.6 is now live at <a href="http://www.andromo.com">www.andromo.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4007" src="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/andromo-coffee-cup-1.jpg?resize=600%2C414&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="600" height="414" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/andromo-coffee-cup-1.jpg?resize=600%2C414&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/andromo-coffee-cup-1.jpg?resize=768%2C530&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/andromo-coffee-cup-1.jpg?resize=1000%2C690&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.andromo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/andromo-coffee-cup-1.jpg?w=1440&amp;ssl=1 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>
